::KitKat::

She went around the entrance of the tunnel.  She didn't like being 
back in the cave.  She knew that it took all the other bots to rescue 
Quickstrike.  She was alone this time and wouldn't have the back up 
if she needed it.  She opened her commlink. "Rowdy, please come in.  
I"m here to help you. Please respond."

she just hoped that the wolfbot who she had fought with earlier 
wouldn't show it's self.
